premise_source_doc_sentence: Marie Antoinette  (  -LSB- ˈmæriˌæntwəˈnɛt -RSB- , -LSB- ˌɑ̃ːntwə - -RSB- , -LSB- ˌɑ̃ːtwə - -RSB- , -LSB- məˈriː - -RSB- -LSB- maʁi ɑ̃twanɛt -RSB- ; born Maria Antonia Josepha Johanna  (  2 November 1755 -- 16 October 1793  )  was the last Queen of France and Navarre before the French Revolution .
